syntax:- <form action="URL" method="GET/POST"><form>
--------

attributes:-
-----------
+ action:- once the from is submitted the action attribute is used to give the server URL.
+ method:- it has two values 
    * get --> the data is visible in URL and not secured.
    * post --> the data is not visible in URL and secured.

note:- by default get method will be there when we create a form.



